    "Bollywood has twisted Holi into a disturbing tale of sexual violence",
    "MAKE IT STOP",
    "\n<p>India&rsquo;s most famously colourful festival has a dark side.</p>\n<p>As the country gears up to celebrate Holi on March 02, stocking up on bags of coloured powders and preparing the traditional <em>gujia</em> sweet, women are still coming to terms with the sheer nastiness of the news that a New Delhi student had balloons <a href=\"https://www.hindustantimes.com/delhi-news/bura-maano-un-holi-hai-lsr-girl-gets-semen-filled-balloons-flung-at-her/story-C4tx7tMDXlV58Ovl0ZVhgM.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">filled with semen</a> thrown on her. While this incident is particularly appalling, it&rsquo;s a reminder of how the joyous occasion makes way for sexual harassment in the garb of uninhibited interactions among strangers. It is normal during the celebrations for complete strangers to douse passersby in water and colours.</p>\n<p>Of course, sexual harassment is cruelly commonplace across India outside of Holi, too. But many women can attest to being particularly targeted at this time. And, often, Bollywood has a lot to do with this.</p>\n<div class=\"inline-ad\" id=\"inline-1218921-1\"></div><p>Besides teaching generations of Indians that stalking is the best way to turn a &ldquo;no&rdquo; into a &ldquo;yes,&rdquo; movies with Holi songs have for decades featured suggestive lyrics that almost normalise sexual harassment, disguising it under bright colours and celebrations. These songs are often accompanied by titillating videos that focus on female stars being chased by their lovers and drenched in colours, despite their protests. Nevertheless, they make it to Holi party playlists every year and contribute to the culture that makes it especially uncomfortable to be a woman out in public at this time of the year.</p>\n<p>Here&rsquo;s some of the biggest culprits:</p>\n<h2>Aaj na Chhodenge from Kati Patang (1970)</h2>\n<div class=\"inline-video\" itemprop=\"video\" itemscope itemtype=\"http://schema.org/VideoObject\"><meta itemprop=\"name\" content=\"Aaj Na Chhodenge - Bollywood Holi Song - Rajesh Khanna &amp; Asha Parekh - Kati Patang\"><meta itemprop=\"description\" content=\"Watch the Holi special song 'Aaj Na Chhodenge' sung by Kishore Kumar and Lata Mangeshkar from the super hit Bollywood movie Kati Patang (1970) starring Rajesh Khanna and Asha Parekh. Music is composed by R.D.Burman and movie Directed by Shakti Samanta.\n\nSubscribe to Rajshri - http://goo.gl/eXlZ3\n\nFollow us on G+ http://plus.google.com/+rajshri\n\nLike us on Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/rajshri\n\nFollow us on Twitter - https://twitter.com/Rajshri\n\nFollow us on Pinterest - http://www.pinterest.com/rajshrivideos\n\nVisit Rajshri's Website - http://www.rajshri.com\"><meta itemprop=\"uploadDate\" content=\"2008-04-01T10:34:20.000Z\"><meta itemprop=\"duration\" content=\"PT4M55S\"><iframe class=\"youtube-player\" type=\"text/html\" width=\"640\" height=\"390\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/hCLW9VOLpuc?version=3&amp;rel=1&amp;fs=1&amp;autohide=2&amp;showsearch=0&amp;showinfo=1&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\"></iframe></div>\n<p>Rajesh Khanna&rsquo;s character says he won&rsquo;t leave alone his lover, played by Asha Parekh, even if her clothes are soaked during the Holi celebrations.</p>\n<h2>Ang se ang lagana from Darr (1993)</h2>\n<div class=\"inline-video\" itemprop=\"video\" itemscope itemtype=\"http://schema.org/VideoObject\"><meta itemprop=\"name\" content=\"Ang Se Ang Lagana - Holi Song | Darr | Shah Rukh Khan | Juhi Chawla | Sunny Deol - &#2361;&#2379;&#2354;&#2368; 2018\"><meta itemprop=\"description\" content=\"&#9658; Subscribe Now: https://goo.gl/xs3mrY &#128276; Stay updated!\n\nMusic, dance, colours, fun &amp; more. Celebrate the festival of colours with this Holi song 'Ang Se Ang Lagana' from 'Darr'. \n\nWatch Full Movie:\nGoogle Play - http://goo.gl/6IWOjR\niTunes - https://goo.gl/n2ukKb\n\nStay in the filmy loop:\n&#9658; Like us on Facebook: https://facebook.com/yrf\n&#9658; Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/yrf\n&#9658; Follow us on Instagram: http://instagram.com/yrf\n\n&#127916; Movie Credits:\nStarring: Shah Rukh Khan, Juhi Chawla, Sunny Deol, Anupam Kher &amp; Tanvi Azmi\nLyrics: Anand Bakshi\nMusic: Shiv-Hari\nStory &amp; Screenplay: Honey Irani\nAssociate Director: Aditya Chopra\nProduced &amp; Directed By: Yash Chopra\nRelease Date: 24 December 1993\n\nSynopsis:\nDARR (Fear) is the villain in every love story. But in Yash Chopra's Darr, fear is the ultimate expression of passion, obsession and sacrifice.\n\nDarr is Rahul's (Shah Rukh Khan) story whose love and obsession for Kiran (Juhi Chawla) frees him from all fears of life and death.\n\nDarr is Sunil's (Sunny Deol) story, whose enduring love and passion for Kiran gives him the courage to face the fear of death.\n\nAnd finally Darr is Kiran's story caught between one man's love and another man's obsession. She fears one and fears for the other. One stands for love and the other for life.\n\nDARR won the National Award for Best Film in 1993 and is remembered for Shah Rukh Khan's mesmerizing performance. International renowned classical music maestros Shiv-Hari composed the haunting melodies of the film.\"><meta itemprop=\"uploadDate\" content=\"2012-03-01T06:40:34.000Z\"><meta itemprop=\"thumbnailUrl\" content=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/bue7fClXlkI/sddefault.jpg\"><meta itemprop=\"duration\" content=\"PT5M51S\"><iframe class=\"youtube-player\" type=\"text/html\" width=\"640\" height=\"390\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/bue7fClXlkI?version=3&amp;rel=1&amp;fs=1&amp;autohide=2&amp;showsearch=0&amp;showinfo=1&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\"></iframe></div>\n<p>In this song, Sunny Deol&rsquo;s character promises to touch every part of his lover&rsquo;s body with his own, and says he&rsquo;s undeterred by even her complaints to the police.</p>\n<h2>Soni soni from Mohabbatein (2000)</h2>\n<div class=\"inline-video\" itemprop=\"video\" itemscope itemtype=\"http://schema.org/VideoObject\"><meta itemprop=\"name\" content=\"Soni Soni - Holi Song | Mohabbatein | Amitabh Bachchan | Shah Rukh Khan | Aishwarya Rai - &#2361;&#2379;&#2354;&#2368; 2018\"><meta itemprop=\"description\" content=\"&#9658; Swag Se Swagat Song: https://youtu.be/xmU0s2QtaEY \n&#9658; Tiger Zinda Hai Trailer: https://youtu.be/ePO5M5DE01I\n&#9658; Subscribe Now: https://goo.gl/xs3mrY &#128276; Stay updated!\n\nHoli is incomplete without song,dance and your Soni. Tease and sprinkle the color of love on your better half! \n \nWatch Full Movie:\n&#9658; Google Play - http://goo.gl/0eY481\n&#9658; iTunes - https://goo.gl/NDJehX\n\n&#127911; Song Credits:\nSong: Soni Soni\nSingers: Udit Narayan, Jaspinder Narula, Udbhav, Manohar Shetty, Ishaan, Shweta Pandit, Sonali Bhatawdekar, Pritha Mazumdar\nMusic: Jatin-Lalit\nLyrics: Anand Bakshi\n\nStay in the filmy loop:\n&#9658; Like us on Facebook: https://facebook.com/yrf\n&#9658; Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/yrf\n&#9658; Follow us on Instagram: http://instagram.com/yrf\n\n&#127916; Movie Credits:\nStarring: Amitabh Bachchan, Shah Rukh Khan, Aishwarya Rai, Uday Chopra, Jugal Hansraj, Jimmy Shergill, Shamita Shetty, Kim Sharma, Preeti Jhangiani\nLyrics: Anand Bakshi\nMusic: Jatin-Lalit\nProduced By: Yash Chopra\nDirected By: Aditya Chopra\nRelease Date: 27 October 2000\n\nSynopsis:\nNational Award winner, Yash Chopra and Aditya Chopra&rsquo;s MOHABBATEIN is a film that portrays the battle between love and fear... A battle between two stubborn men and their opposing beliefs.\n\nRaj Aryan (Shah Rukh Khan), who stands for love, he would go to any lengths for it.\n\nNarayan Shankar (Amitabh Bachchan - voted the Millennium star in the BBC polls) a strict disciplinarian as the head of India&rsquo;s most prestigious educational institute who stands for fear, he believes that love leads to pain and weakness.\n\nIt is also the story of 3 young men and women who have to learn to follow their hearts against all the odds and the outcome of their love stories that will decide what will finally triumph love or fear.\"><meta itemprop=\"uploadDate\" content=\"2012-03-01T07:37:30.000Z\"><meta itemprop=\"thumbnailUrl\" content=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/OpLD97fG9Hw/sddefault.jpg\"><meta itemprop=\"duration\" content=\"PT9M11S\"><iframe class=\"youtube-player\" type=\"text/html\" width=\"640\" height=\"390\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/OpLD97fG9Hw?version=3&amp;rel=1&amp;fs=1&amp;autohide=2&amp;showsearch=0&amp;showinfo=1&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\"></iframe></div>\n<p>Here the leading women, who make their entrance dressed in pristine white clothes, are forcibly coloured by their lovers who croon that their &ldquo;abuses&rdquo; can&rsquo;t stop the men from loving them.</p>\n<h2>Do me a favour, let&rsquo;s play holi from Waqt (2005)</h2>\n<div class=\"inline-video\" itemprop=\"video\" itemscope itemtype=\"http://schema.org/VideoObject\"><meta itemprop=\"name\" content='\"Do Me A Favour Lets Play Holi\" Waqt- The Race Against Time, Priyanka Chopra, Akshay Kumar'><meta itemprop=\"description\" content=\"Song - Do Me A Favour Lets Play Holi \nFilm - Waqt- The Race Against Time\nSinger - Anu Malik, Sunidhi Chauhan\nLyricist - Sameer\nMusic Director - Anu Malik\nArtist - Akshay Kumar, Priyanka Chopra, Amitabh Bachchan, Shefali Shah\nMusic On - T-Series\"><meta itemprop=\"uploadDate\" content=\"2011-05-30T13:31:22.000Z\"><meta itemprop=\"thumbnailUrl\" content=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/uyh9jYSGpCg/sddefault.jpg\"><meta itemprop=\"duration\" content=\"PT6M2S\"><iframe class=\"youtube-player\" type=\"text/html\" width=\"640\" height=\"390\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/uyh9jYSGpCg?version=3&amp;rel=1&amp;fs=1&amp;autohide=2&amp;showsearch=0&amp;showinfo=1&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\"></iframe></div>\n<p>In this song, actress Priyanka Chopra&rsquo;s character bemoans being followed by her lover, and urges him not to touch her blouse. This, however, doesn&rsquo;t stop Akshay Kumar&rsquo;s character from pelting her with colours.</p>\n<h2>Balam pichkari from Yeh Jawaani Hai Deewani (2013)</h2>\n<div class=\"inline-video\" itemprop=\"video\" itemscope itemtype=\"http://schema.org/VideoObject\"><meta itemprop=\"name\" content=\"Balam Pichkari Full Song Video Yeh Jawaani Hai Deewani | Ranbir Kapoor, Deepika Padukone\"><meta itemprop=\"description\" content='Enjoy \"Balam Pichkari full song\" video in voice of prolific singers Vishal Dadlani, Shalmali Kholgade from bolckbuster hindi movie Yeh Jawaani Hai Deewani directed by Ayan Mukerji starring Ranbir Kapoor, Deepika Padukone, Aditya Roy Kapoor, Kalki Koechlin.\n\nSong: \"Balam Pichkari\"\nMusic: Pritam Chakraborty\nSinger: Vishal Dadlani, Shalmali Kholgade \nMovie: Yeh Jawaani Hai Deewani (2013)\nDirector: Ayan Mukerji\nCast: Ranbir Kapoor, Deepika Padukone, Aditya Roy Kapoor, Kalki Koechlin\nMusic on T-Series\n\nSet it as your caller tune SMS YJHD4 to 54646\nhttp://bit.ly/1JJFI6B\nhttp://goo.gl/qSDXpw\n\nBuy it from iTunes: https://geo.itunes.apple.com/in/album/yeh-jawaani-hai-deewani-original/id642380120?ls=1\n\nSUBSCRIBE T-Series channel for unlimited entertainment\nhttp://www.youtube.com/tseries\n\nCircle us on G+ \nhttp://www.google.com/+tseriesmusic\n\nLike us on Facebook\nhttp://www.facebook.com/tseriesmusic\n\nFollow us\nhttp://www.twitter.com/_Tseries'><meta itemprop=\"uploadDate\" content=\"2013-06-22T13:00:04.000Z\"><meta itemprop=\"thumbnailUrl\" content=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/0WtRNGubWGA/sddefault.jpg\"><meta itemprop=\"duration\" content=\"PT4M20S\"><iframe class=\"youtube-player\" type=\"text/html\" width=\"640\" height=\"390\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/0WtRNGubWGA?version=3&amp;rel=1&amp;fs=1&amp;autohide=2&amp;showsearch=0&amp;showinfo=1&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\"></iframe></div>\n<p>While Deepika Padukone&rsquo;s character has a little more agency than previous Bollywood heroines in this recent movie, she doesn&rsquo;t escape being objectified in its Holi song, and facing what surely should count as sexual harassment when Ranbir Kapoor&rsquo;s character playfully peers at her cleavage.</p>\n<h2>Go pagal from Jolly LLB 2 (2017)</h2>\n<div class=\"inline-video\" itemprop=\"video\" itemscope itemtype=\"http://schema.org/VideoObject\"><meta itemprop=\"name\" content=\"Jolly LLB 2 | GO PAGAL Video Song | Akshay Kumar,Huma Qureshi | Manj Musik Raftaar, Nindy Kaur\"><meta itemprop=\"description\" content='Presenting the First Video Song \"GO PAGAL\" from the Upcoming Bollywood movie Jolly LLB 2, the movie is produced by Fox Star Studios and directed by Subhash Kapoor, Jolly LL.B 2 starring Akshay Kumar, Huma Qureshi, Annu Kapoor and Saurabh Shukla is slated to release on 10th February 2017.\n\nSong &#9835;Also Available On:\niTunes: http://bit.ly/Go_Pagal_JollyLLB2_iTunes\nHungama: http://bit.ly/Go_Pagal_JollyLLB2_Hungama\nSaavn: http://bit.ly/Go_Pagal_JollyLLB2_Saavn\n\nFor Caller Tunes :\nGo Pagal http://bit.ly/2iHbDuF\nGo Pagal - Tere Iraado http://bit.ly/2jdF62F\n\nSet \"Go Pagal \" as your caller tune - sms JOLLY1 To 54646\nSet \"Go Pagal - Tere Iraado\" as your caller tune - sms JOLLY2 To 54646\n________________________________________\nOperator Codes: \n1.Go Pagal\nVodafone Subscribers Dial 5379088037\nAirtel Subscribers Dial 5432116076231\nReliance Subscribers SMS CT 9088037 to 51234\nIdea Subscribers Dial 567899088037\nTata DoCoMo Subscribers dial 5432119088037\nAircel Subscribers sms DT 6526098  To 53000\nBSNL (South / East) Subscribers sms BT 9088037 To 56700\nBSNL (North / West) Subscribers sms BT 6526098 To 56700\nVirgin Subscribers sms TT 9088037 To 58475\nMTS Subscribers  sms CT 6525678 to 55777\nVideocon Subscribers dial 54321100518718\nTelenor Subscribers dial 50016526029\nMTNL Subscribers sms PT 9088037 To 56789\n\n2. Go Pagal - Tere Iraado\nVodafone Subscribers Dial 5379088038\nAirtel Subscribers Dial 5432116076074\nReliance Subscribers SMS CT 9088038 to 51234\nIdea Subscribers Dial 567899088038\nTata DoCoMo Subscribers dial 5432119088038\nAircel Subscribers sms DT 6526099  To 53000\nBSNL (South / East) Subscribers sms BT 9088038 To 56700\nBSNL (North / West) Subscribers sms BT 6526099 To 56700\nVirgin Subscribers sms TT 9088038 To 58475\nMTS Subscribers  sms CT 6525679 to 55777\nVideocon Subscribers dial 54321100518719\nTelenor Subscribers dial 50016526030\nMTNL Subscribers sms PT 9088038 To 56789\n\nSong Credits: \nSong: Go Pagal\nMovie: Jolly Llb 2\nSinger: Raftaar,Nindy Kaur\nAdditional Vocals: Girish Nakod,Manj Musik\nMusic Director: Manj Musik\nCo-Composed By Nilesh Patel\nLyrics: Manj Musik,Raftaar\nBacking vocals by - Girish Nakod, Manj Musik\nComposed &amp; Arranged by - Manj Musik\nCo-composed by &ndash; Nilesh Patel\nCo-Arranged by - Nilesh Patel &amp; Girish Nakod\nMusic On T-Series\n\nEnjoy and stay connected with us!!\n\nSubscribe to T-Series Channel for unlimited entertainment\nhttp://www.youtube.com/user/tseries?sub_confirmation=1\n\nCircle us on G+\nhttp://www.google.com/+tseriesmusic\n\nLike us on Facebook\nhttp://www.facebook.com/tseriesmusic\n\nFollow us on\nhttp://www.twitter.com/tseries\n\nFollow us on\nhttp://www.instagram.com/tseries.official\n\nFind us on\nhttp://pinterest.com/tseries\n\n----------------------------------------------'><meta itemprop=\"uploadDate\" content=\"2017-01-04T05:32:33.000Z\"><meta itemprop=\"thumbnailUrl\" content=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/iFARFbekNl8/sddefault.jpg\"><meta itemprop=\"duration\" content=\"PT2M20S\"><iframe class=\"youtube-player\" type=\"text/html\" width=\"640\" height=\"390\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/iFARFbekNl8?version=3&amp;rel=1&amp;fs=1&amp;autohide=2&amp;showsearch=0&amp;showinfo=1&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\"></iframe></div>\n<p>The heroine here protests at being followed by a man. But the song brushes aside her plaints saying there&rsquo;s no need to get upset because, after all, it&rsquo;s Holi and it&rsquo;s &ldquo;no fun&rdquo; if you get upset.</p>\n",
